{"tid":1810997,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 國務院-免去王志民中聯辦主任職務-前山西省委書記駱惠寧接任","createTime":"2020-01-04T10:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T22:38:40.000Z","uid":61161,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6944204028b9056cd51c02549833d5b0a35da6","tid":1810997,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"新華社北京1月4日消息，國務院任免國家工作人員。任命朱詠雷為國家廣播電視總局副局長；任命駱惠寧為中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任。免去王志民的中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任職務。<br />\n資料顯示，駱惠寧是浙江義烏人，1954年出生於安徽省當塗縣。1970年9月參加工作，1982年3月加入中國共產黨，中國人民大學經濟學院政治經濟學專業畢業，在職研究生學歷，經濟學博士，中共第十七屆中央候補委員，第十八、十九屆中央委員，曾任中共青海省委書記、中共山西省委書記。<br />\n<br />\n據來自北京最權威的消息，這次調整是因應近期香港情況的變化，委任更符合香港現實發展的官員擔當中聯辦的工作，所以對中聯辦主任人選進行調整。北京最權威消息表示，中央對「王志民同志的工作充分肯定」，顯然沒有任何問責的意味。駱已經到了正部級退休年齡，最近剛被任命為人大財經委員會副主任委員，今次以66歲之齡，突然從人大轉赴非常時期的香港。"},{"pid":"d3b0fc56b6fbe31b01423bd41e2c3e23a8b7fb7b","tid":1810997,"uid":100438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9db977bd0ad1e399535b292309826bf2b99f94","tid":1810997,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d0753bec48152a216be0f54ca032390c83b474","tid":1810997,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"條友咩背景?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e1bf702e5af03f2d998d92d8cab89c63e890e7","tid":1810997,"uid":4174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"王志民由澳門黎冇耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下場會唔會好似上一任澳門中聯辦主任。。。"},{"pid":"4d4c3e973dac0cf269a447f6b33822569e7ca707","tid":1810997,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"中央對「王志民同志的工作充分肯定」<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bb067a97059a0ba0b4b23e6caeb9a6eb327cff","tid":1810997,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"仆街,呢條友手段係點有無人知"},{"pid":"6a0d819f06a3e581342b6d199e731baad9912cf4","tid":1810997,"uid":4503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/622/19322.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochweekly.com%2Fb5%2F622%2F19322.htm&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=f566125b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/622/19322.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n江派？"},{"pid":"0937a9106666567a8503cd7cb6e2b0a799147d6c","tid":1810997,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"王志民手足上黎連登報個平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33780ed02d9d706828cddad5c619b7ec73f8c73","tid":1810997,"uid":33099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07bb067a97059a0ba0b4b23e6caeb9a6eb327cff","tid":1810997,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"仆街,呢條友手段係點有無人知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"唔重要<br />\n<br />\n邊個做我地真正對手都係維尼"},{"pid":"0546ee5ff099a5f2c7b6902f56af7848c71b1b2d","tid":1810997,"uid":61161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"補多篇最近嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧被免職　省委書記一職由樓陽生升任<br />\n2019年11月30日(六) 15:40<br />\n<br />\n內媒周六（30日）報道，山西省委書記、常委駱惠寧已被免職，書記一職由山西省委副書記樓陽生升任；報道未有提及駱惠寧是否另有任用。<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，駱惠寧生於1954年，安徽當塗縣人，1982年畢業於安徽大學；1995年，駱惠寧任安徽省政府副秘書長、辦公廳主任，兩年後任省政府秘書長。1998年，駱惠寧任巢湖市委書記，一年多後，於1999年任安徽省委常委、宣傳部部長。2010年，駱惠寧調任青海省省長。2013年，出任青海省委書記。2016年，駱惠寧調任山西省委書記直至被免職。<br />\n<br />\n另外，樓陽生出生於1959年，浙江浦江縣人，浙江師範學院畢業。先後擔任過浙江省龍游縣委常委、縣宣傳部部長、金華市委副書記、政法委書記（正廳級）、市委黨校校長、麗水市委書記、海南省委常委、組織部部長，省教育工委書記；2014年6月開始擔任山西省委副書記。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191130/mobile/bkn-20191130154057034-1130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191130154057034-1130_00952_001.html&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=613acd55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191130/mobile/bkn-20191130154057034-1130_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8a9bdab29a38bf4fb01d18880600ad1bf3e7ecd7","tid":1810997,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07bb067a97059a0ba0b4b23e6caeb9a6eb327cff","tid":1810997,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"仆街,呢條友手段係點有無人知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"山西刀削麵  快 狠  準"},{"pid":"569fcdcc8beb20f976aa2eb36ef87b3664b17875","tid":1810997,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"之前幾任中聯辦主任升之前都有做過同香港有關嘅職位，呢個都算係空降"},{"pid":"64d0f8eed8647aa27f85eab0846099a4dc0ca91c","tid":1810997,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"569fcdcc8beb20f976aa2eb36ef87b3664b17875","tid":1810997,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"之前幾任中聯辦主任升之前都有做過同香港有關嘅職位，呢個都算係空降"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"咁無乜路捉喎"},{"pid":"4f6d6b0361a072aa94e2578ab41d8d81287429d6","tid":1810997,"uid":196961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0d819f06a3e581342b6d199e731baad9912cf4","tid":1810997,"uid":4503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/622/19322.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochweekly.com%2Fb5%2F622%2F19322.htm&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=f566125b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/622/19322.htm</a><br /